    <comment>update to 3.6.7 - upstream security release fixing 16 CVEs (remote buffer overflows CVE-2026-50580/-35336/-50713, use-after-free CVE-2026-50579, X.509 CA-bit forgery CVE-2026-49300, RSA/ECC side channels, and more). ABI-compatible: sonames unchanged. Changelog also references the openSUSE bugs for the 3.6.6 CVE batch (boo#1261448-boo#1261527) this package carries. Built + ctest green on aarch64.</comment>
